---
source: crates/runtime/tests/metadata/mod.rs
expression: explain_met_location_filtered
---
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: met_location.id ASC NULLS LAST, met_location.location ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |   Filter: met_location.location = Utf8("s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet")                                                                                         |
|               |     TableScan: met_location projection=[id, value, year, month, day, location], partial_filters=[met_location.location = Utf8("s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet")] |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [id@0 ASC NULLS LAST, location@5 ASC NULLS LAST]                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |   SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |     FilterExec: location@5 = s3://spiceai-public-datasets/hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet                                                                                                      |
|               |       RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |           DataSourceExec: file_groups={1 group: [[hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet]]}, projection=[id, value, year, month, day, location], file_type=parquet                                    |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
